<topic template="Default" status="Needs Review" modified="2026-04-07T14:01:12.732Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>3.3 Confirming Pallet Number</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">确认托盘编号</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="19. APC - Pallet No. .png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">该字段显示工作台一侧的托盘编号。关于工作台一侧，</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:11px; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:11px;">CW (LS103) 信号为 ON，则工作台一侧的托盘为 &quot;1&quot;</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">CCW（LS102）信号为 ON，则工作台一侧的托盘为 &quot;2&quot;</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">当 APC 操作正在进行时，信号 LS102 / LS103 均为 &quot;0&quot;，则托盘编号显示为 &quot;0&quot;。</para>
  </body>
</topic>
